{"tid":1947640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日副首相麻生太郎：台灣在這疫情中處理得最好的國家","createTime":"2020-03-28T12:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T13:06:30.000Z","uid":191812,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f8958f5455131e1ead8fea6e91ddc14cc1714b78","tid":1947640,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）疫情爆發，世界衛生組織（who）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）的防疫作法引發抱怨，對此先前在公開場合直呼「武漢病毒」的日本副首相麻生太郎，不僅回應有很多人說要把世界衛生組織（WHO）改名叫「中國衛生組織」（CHO），也大讚台灣防疫做得好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/27/2475780-XXL.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2F2475780-XXL.jpg&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=09430a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2F2475780-XXL.jpg&h=cf16d21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/27/2475780-XXL.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n▲日本副首相麻生太郎。（圖／翻攝自日本參議院官網）<br />\n<br />\n日本參院財政金融委員會26日開會，提及網路上有人認為WHO沒保持政治上中立，連署要求秘書長譚德塞下台一事。對此副首相麻生太郎回應，WHO前任秘書長陳馮富珍也是中國人，先前也引發不少抱怨。<br />\n<br />\n麻生太郎指出，因為譚德塞之前說中國武漢沒有病毒，現在有很多人說要WHO改名為CHO，要是他早點坦承疫情很嚴重，各國就能及時做好應對措施，現在也不會有那麼多人反彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/27/2475782-XXL.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2F2475782-XXL.jpg&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=3816aeda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2F2475782-XXL.jpg&h=232d4c80\" target=\"_blank\">https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/27/2475782-XXL.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n▲麻生太郎稱台灣是國家。（圖／翻攝自日本參議院官網）<br />\n<br />\n麻生太郎表示，WHO是一個很重要的組織，但台灣是應對這次疫情最好也最早的國家，卻不讓台灣加入。麻生太郎也嘲諷，他把台灣稱為國家，共產黨一定又會開罵、逼他下台，「所以我該說台灣『地區』因應得最好」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qeeZWVl60uQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqeeZWVl60uQ&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b9cde847\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qeeZWVl60uQ</a>"},{"pid":"db1e07646693378dd221d316d3cdde547729a1c7","tid":1947640,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"好串"},{"pid":"7ac730c304a330eaeab62b3dc268f3d8a365a901","tid":1947640,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"中國:多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbc0ae32202497aedab21b629202a5da5191f79","tid":1947640,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"講事實姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41bb43904f63fc6f3468d22331cad69ab363b16","tid":1947640,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"知道小支支最憎嗰樣就講嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f43e4311a9b8fce9310553dd5d2daf285296937","tid":1947640,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"當共產黨傻仔咁笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736046c55c2a02690b01f2c9aa7b8dcedd95fb68","tid":1947640,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"麻生太郎不嬲都係反支"},{"pid":"d4506f71b3cf3b9a4d8277fb479cf66eec0f6559","tid":1947640,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b0d98a2be6361b22c7cdf21d9a8c879415db44","tid":1947640,"uid